comments: It was easy enough to learn the words, since there were only four.  I just memorized them and didn't write anything down or anything like that.  I wish the words changed a bit to distinguish the colors, but I suspect that is somehow the point.  The second part was very hard since you only had a 1/4 chance of picking the correct one, even if you knew the word.  I tried to track which colors had already been used, with limited success.
